        <section id="section_ukg_jvy_c5b">
            <p><indexterm>hardware requirements for AWS EC2</indexterm> Refer to the tables below
                for determining the optimal number of agents that your StellarOne server deployment
                can manage on the AWS EC2 platform.<note id="note_s13_b2d_mvb">
                    <p>Please refer to <xref href="https://aws.amazon.com/ec2/instance-types/"
                            format="html" scope="external">Amazon EC2 Instance Types</xref> for
                        specifications of the instance types.</p>
                </note></p>
